line_1: Except such slaves as bow the knee to Baal —
line_2: Brandishing high the scorpion scourage o'er all,

line_1: Osiris left his Nile, and thund'ring Baal
line_2: The rock, whence Arnon's plentous waters fall.

line_1: And curling Frankincense ascends to Baal.
line_2: With the Chaldean's Charms her Rites prevail;
